Properties.commandText:
CREATE TABLE [RolePermissions] (
    [RoleId] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [PermissionId] int NOT NULL,
    [ModuleId] int NOT NULL,
    [SubModuleId] int NOT NULL,
    [Id] int NOT NULL,
    [PageId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_RolePermissions] PRIMARY KEY ([RoleId], [PermissionId], [ModuleId], [SubModuleId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_AspNetRoles_RoleId] FOREIGN KEY ([RoleId]) REFERENCES [AspNetRoles] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_Modules_ModuleId] FOREIGN KEY ([ModuleId]) REFERENCES [Modules] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_Pages_PageId] FOREIGN KEY ([PageId]) REFERENCES [Pages] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_PermissionTyepe_PermissionId] FOREIGN KEY ([PermissionId]) REFERENCES [PermissionTyepe] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_SubModules_SubModuleId] FOREIGN KEY ([SubModuleId]) REFERENCES [SubModules] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [RolePermissions] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [RoleId] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [PermissionId] int NOT NULL,
    [ModuleId] int NOT NULL,
    [SubModuleId] int NOT NULL,
    [PageId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_RolePermissions] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_AspNetRoles_RoleId] FOREIGN KEY ([RoleId]) REFERENCES [AspNetRoles] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_Modules_ModuleId] FOREIGN KEY ([ModuleId]) REFERENCES [Modules] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_Pages_PageId] FOREIGN KEY ([PageId]) REFERENCES [Pages] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_PermissionTyepe_PermissionId] FOREIGN KEY ([PermissionId]) REFERENCES [PermissionTyepe] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RolePermissions_SubModules_SubModuleId] FOREIGN KEY ([SubModuleId]) REFERENCES [SubModules] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
